<doc id="321658" url="https://ml.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=321658" title="Mi 26">
Mi 26

 
! colspan="2" style="text-align: center; font-size: large; padding-bottom: 0.3em;" | Mi-26
! Role
! National origin 
! Manufacturer
! Designer
! First flight
! Introduction
